{"_id":"0DCFugl8E3Uc0oPB","name":"Ganger","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>It's hard to make a living in the Chorus, and they forced you to make a bad choice. Robbing is simple and straightforward. A gun is a great persuader. The difficult bit is living long enough to spend what you have - those police and Nova Guard are everywhere, and some people seem to frown on a gang of ruffians. What is the galaxy coming to?</p>\n<p>Equipment: A old but reliable multigun (L2d6+1P), padded armour, a helmet and an old shield generator (light armour). A breather facemask. A letter from a victim to their lover, too poetic to discard.</p>\n<p><strong>What did you do? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Refused to enlist in the Nova Guard.</li>\n<li>Threw rocks at a Merchant Combine representative who'd bought your land.</li>\n<li>Stole coin from a drunk system Lord.</li>\n<li>Killed an artisan in a brawl over the local skimball team.</li>\n<li>No idea, they wouldn't say.</li>\n<li>Handed out seditious material for the Krebix revolution.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Who hunts you? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Nova Guard, always watchful.</li>\n<li>Hafo Lux, who hates you.</li>\n<li>Your family, eager to have you back.</li>\n<li>An Ion Priest, for revenge.</li>\n<li>The Bakkus pilgrims, you stole a relic.</li>\n<li>No one, you're lucky so far!</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223592,"modifiedTime":1662411891419,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"9AcW2jhNRquSx7AX","name":"Bounty Hunter","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>You keep to yourself. Your face is enough to keep most people away. You have a knack for finding people, people that don't want to be found. Mainly that's a result of knowing the right people - or the wrong people, as most would see it. But you're handy with a blade too, as most of the people you are looking for will do a lot not to get found.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A serrated blade (S1d6+2S), under jacket body plates and shield projector (modest armour), a python pistol (S1d6+2P). A database of faces and names for you to look out for.</p>\n<p><strong>Who you have caught? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The murderer of the Messiah of Krebix.</li>\n<li>Deserters from the ruins of Damas IV.</li>\n<li>Your sister. Don't ask.</li>\n<li>Deserters from the Nova Guard.</li>\n<li>The wrong person, but don't tell.</li>\n<li>The agitator Hemlock, from the mines of Kex II.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Who you're searching for? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Rello system poisoner Kacis.</li>\n<li>The machine agent FeX44.</li>\n<li>The mad Ion Priest Tolbera Frey.</li>\n<li>The barbarian Queen Tamulan, a revolutionary.</li>\n<li>A reason to hope, in a dark galaxy.</li>\n<li>A way out and into the light.</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223594,"modifiedTime":1662411891420,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"BsEx42h412O9MtcG","name":"Bodyguard","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>You've guarded everyone from merchants in fear of rivals to rich Lords of core worlds after some fun in the rougher parts of the galaxy. You know how to keep quiet and look mean - all you need, most of the time. But if things get out of hand and you need to pull a weapon, you're ready for that too. Never lost a client. So far.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A nox-rifle (M2d6P), armoured bodysuit and shield projector (modest armour), power baton (S1d6+1C). A video of your mother, which makes you cry.</p>\n<p><strong>Who you have protected? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Lord Hastamir during the revolt on Malbaada II</li>\n<li>Ariol Zee, the holostar and ace reporter.</li>\n<li>The Ion Priest Tolbera Frey.</li>\n<li>The Smuggler Fessus, a bloated fool.</li>\n<li>The crime lord Xxenin, in the port of Sorrow.</li>\n<li>The Merchant Hafo Lux, during the grain riots.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>A secret you know about them (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>They are actually a series of clones.</li>\n<li>They don't exist, it's all a front.</li>\n<li>They once killed their lover.</li>\n<li>Where they keep their ship.</li>\n<li>Who made them, and from what.</li>\n<li>That they have no secrets. Terrifying.</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223597,"modifiedTime":1662411891421,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"EBxJzHRIMXGR4CGs","name":"Thief","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>So you steal. Nothing wrong with that - it's an honest profession. You take what you need and spend it, you're just redistributing wealth and keeping the economy ticking over. You only take from the rich. Well, mostly from the rich. Needs must eh? Can't be too picky.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A small concealable laser pistol (S1d6+1E), lock-picking electronics, a powered pry bar and a full but light trench coat to hide it all in. A sack for you gains, no doubt ill-gotten.</p>\n<p><strong>What or who have you robbed? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>House Freyne, they were displeased.</li>\n<li>Grom the Elder, he didn't even notice.</li>\n<li>I'm telling you nothing.</li>\n<li>The Pleasure Hive of Inux Prime, interesting stuff there!</li>\n<li>A Merchant Combine Lord, big mistake.</li>\n<li>The local Nova Guard captain, an easy mark.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Who wants you dead? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Merchant Combine, they don't appreciate artistry.</li>\n<li>The thieves' guild, they charge taxes.</li>\n<li>Your father, you disgrace his name.</li>\n<li>No one, I'm innocent!</li>\n<li>The judge at Damas IV, you escaped.</li>\n<li>I said I'm telling you nothing!</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223600,"modifiedTime":1662411891422,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"GRTMQiKs32tBl6l0","name":"Pirate","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>Whether by coercion, ill fortune or bad judgement, you ended up prowling the spaceways under a stern Captain who seemed fated to become the scourge of known space. That's over now, but you're haunted by the blood and fury of ship-to-ship battles and boarding actions, so far from the epic adventures your crewmates sang of.</p>\n<p>Equipment: Armoured spacesuit (modest armour), disruptor pistol (M2d6E), energy mace (M1d6+1E), implosion charge (S2d6E), hip flask of Jelaxi grog.</p>\n<p><strong>What have you plundered? (roll&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The wreck of the Shazanthi Queen.</li>\n<li>Cadence courier speeding to Pyrras Minor.</li>\n<li>Artworks from Lord Tern's orbital retreat.</li>\n<li>Arms shipments to Krebix revolutionaries.</li>\n<li>Hegemony waystation, never again!</li>\n<li>Pilgrim convoy on the Bakkus Rim.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What made you leave the crew? (roll&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Captain replaced you all with robots.</li>\n<li>Ship was destroyed, you took the only life pod.</li>\n<li>Merchant Combine put a price on your head.</li>\n<li>Captain went mad, saw something out in the Warp.</li>\n<li>Nova Guard always one step ahead of you.</li>\n<li>You promised your dying lover you would.</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223601,"modifiedTime":1662411891423,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"IumcT8kNRdTToE2U","name":"Scout","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>You are a trailblazing pioneer exploring the edges of the Chorus of a Million Worlds. You are truly in your element when hacking through an alien jungle; trekking across the black sands of a lifeless desert; or diving the depths of an ice-covered ocean on some forgotten moon. There's a whole universe out there to explore, and you're just the scout to do it!</p>\n<p>Equipment: Vibro-Machete (M1d6+3S), portable wrist-mounted nav-comp, explorator fieldwear (including really, really good boots), Laser sniping rifle (M2d6+1E).</p>\n<p><strong>What places have you explored? (roll&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The acid-rain drenched jungles of Kisshtak.</li>\n<li>The hateful ice-world of Tzur</li>\n<li>The impressive ruins of Silence IV.</li>\n<li>The razor-sands of Black Amathrys.</li>\n<li>The green worlds of the Rhiannon System.</li>\n<li>The earthquake-riven mountains of Camborr.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What did you discover? (roll&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Coordinates of a secret warp route.</li>\n<li>The location of a world rich in rare ores.</li>\n<li>Knowledge of a lost feudal house, changed after years of isolation.</li>\n<li>Tactical readouts of a deadly star-system.</li>\n<li>A terrifying species lurking in the cold.</li>\n<li>A bizarre disease, toxin or symbiote. You might be infected...</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223602,"modifiedTime":1662411891424,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"JLTEy7n19PlnT6AG","name":"Diplomat","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>In the fractured Chorus, not everyone bows to their betters, and warfare can be so... blunt. Your job is to find a peaceful means of getting everyone talking. Tireless patience and the ability to listen are essential, and sometimes a blade is required to settle those formal duels. The food is also good.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A uniform of the diplomatic corps. A datapad of history to pick up the nuances of local events, a duelling sword (M2d6P). Holofilms of your favourite action heroes, something to get lost in.</p>\n<p><strong>Where have you worked? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Queen Tamulan's official surrender.</li>\n<li>The aftermath of the Krebix atrocity.</li>\n<li>The Nova Guard deserters' mass suicide. Messy.</li>\n<li>The Lox transgression, with no blood shed.</li>\n<li>Nowhere you can talk about.</li>\n<li>The Jewel, corrupt heart of the Chorus.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What went wrong? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>No one ever listens. Ever.</li>\n<li>You lost the duel to decide the mission.</li>\n<li>You got drunk and missed the peace signing.</li>\n<li>Everything. Always.</li>\n<li>Nothing went wrong. Who's been talking?</li>\n<li>They say I stole from the diplomatic fund. Prove it I say!</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223603,"modifiedTime":1662411891425,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"O6WJBikoxhIg5sJm","name":"Pilot","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>Destined for glory, you passed the piloting academy's entrance exams with relative ease. Of course, your family always pass, having connections and hailing from such a revered lineage. Unfortunately, when you fell from grace your allowance halted and those who previously revelled in your company now disdain you. Chin up though, you'll soon get back on top where you belong!</p>\n<p>Equipment: crisply-pressed bodysuit and matching jacket with piping and academy insignia, cravat with family crest, shiny high boots, spotless gloves, ceremonial energy sword (M2d6+1E), an electronic journal of your travels.</p>\n<p><strong>What did you learn at the academy? (roll&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The family trees of major feudal houses, thrilling.</li>\n<li>How to mix cocktails while reciting poetry.</li>\n<li>Dangerous yet effective flight stunts.</li>\n<li>How to talk your way out of a fight.</li>\n<li>The eight duelling stances of the Arano.</li>\n<li>How to talk your way into a fight.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Why were you asked to leave? (roll&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>)</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Stealing a shuttle to win a drunken wager.</li>\n<li>You injured some minor noble when sparring.</li>\n<li>Crashing that prototype starfighter.</li>\n<li>Seducing your tutor's intended.</li>\n<li>Insulting visiting dignitaries.</li>\n<li>Ultimately, no-one likes a show-off.</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223605,"modifiedTime":1662411891426,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"VGnYvS9CzxOy5i2H","name":"Exterminator","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>Vermin. Out there, always, eating away at the fabric of civilisation. One day they'll overrun everything and be all that's left in the Chorus. Not today though, you've bills to pay and much as you hate your job, you hate the vermin more.</p>\n<p>Equipment: Reinforced bodysuit (Light armour), filter mask, tool harness, extendible energy prod (S1d6+1E), net, toxic lures, flask of soup.</p>\n<p><strong>Where was the last infestation? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Cramped vents of the Hovash Lunar Convent.</li>\n<li>Orbital laboratory NX-6, life support had failed.</li>\n<li>Vadain Leisure Park, the day before it opened.</li>\n<li>Engine room of the spaceliner Meikas Orchid.</li>\n<li>Lord Zeph's sub-aqua chalet complex.</li>\n<li>Downtown Roux City, thriving in the squalor.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What did you exterminate? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Caustic spungworms, they burn through anything.</li>\n<li>Psionic slimes that when prodded screamed in your mind.</li>\n<li>Encroaching crystal lattice, covering everything.</li>\n<li>Warp krill that attach to ships, and mutate in atmosphere.</li>\n<li>A poisonous spitting bush, will root down anywhere.</li>\n<li>Energy moths, causing systems to fail.</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223608,"modifiedTime":1662411891427,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"X9xpYRLcw5lpFm8z","name":"Warp Touched","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>The warp sings through your skull. Patterns emerge, glyphs redolent with power. But it also threatens to blow your mind. The strain is evident, and people shy away from you. Such is the price of power, raw and unrefined. If only it didn't hurt so much, the power would be worth it.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A cloak with mathematical emblems. A metal staff affixed with an opening eye, and some books on warp theory. Pills and tinctures to ease the pounding headaches. One randomly determined glyph.</p>\n<p><strong>Where have you been? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Jewel of the Chorus, you were shunned.</li>\n<li>The cathedral of the Ion Priests on Hax Prime.</li>\n<li>The fighting maze of Fellus IV.</li>\n<li>The blackened warp roads, never again.</li>\n<li>Nowhere worth visiting.</li>\n<li>The inside of a Pullxi slaveship - you escaped.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What have you seen? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>A warp lord burning with unrestrained power.</li>\n<li>A warp beast tearing a ship in two.</li>\n<li>The look of fear in the eyes of others.</li>\n<li>Dreams of your own death.</li>\n<li>The beautiful fractal patterns of the warp.</li>\n<li>Visions of priests chanting in a golden cave.</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223610,"modifiedTime":1662411891427,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"Xa41TL862dMRmv35","name":"Miner","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>Asteroids and moons are dangerous places, but they can be full of treasure - ores, metals... even alien artefacts. You're experienced at digging those treasures out for profit. There's money to be made in the dead rocks that orbit distant suns.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A mining drill (S1d6+1P), a mining space suit (medium armour), a short range transport ship for moving that ore about. A carving of a mine spirit made from the tusk of an Edletodont, said to ward off the ghosts of long-dead aliens.</p>\n<p><strong>What have you dug up? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>)</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Zeorite, an ore for making metallic foams.</li>\n<li>Good old iron ore, for making weapons.</li>\n<li>Crystal shards impregnated with alien data, the Ion priests pay well.</li>\n<li>Nothing but dirt and ghosts.</li>\n<li>The buried treasure of lost alien race.</li>\n<li>The entrance to a tomb, vacuum-sealed and rotten.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What have you seen? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>)</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Nova Guard destroy a space yacht, for no discernible reason.</li>\n<li>The skull of a warp dragon, long dead.</li>\n<li>Murder in the black depths, out of sight.</li>\n<li>An alien city, lost to the depths of time.</li>\n<li>Warp ghosts drifting from the walls.</li>\n<li>A shrine to an outlawed god, deserted.</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223611,"modifiedTime":1662411891428,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"Xs9rdf4uoRxh3BSq","name":"Scientist","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>The universe is full of amazing sights, and you intend to see as many as you can before you die. Understanding the very nature of the cosmos is your calling, and no amount of danger from pirates, monsters or warp beasts will stop you. You're already sweating at the thought of all those pirates. Gulp.</p>\n<p>Equipment: Fine clothes, a datapad chock full of obtuse scientific works, a multirecorder and specimen kit. A letter of introduction from your university, which perplexingly no-one has heard of. A micro-pistol (S1d6P), which you've never used.</p>\n<p><strong>What do you study? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>)</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Warp fluctuations from positronic emanations.</li>\n<li>Xeno-biology of large-scale hunters.</li>\n<li>Warp drive co-locational theory.</li>\n<li>Everything, just not that well.</li>\n<li>DNA and subvective prion transmission.</li>\n<li>Are you trying to steal my research?</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What have you discovered? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>)</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Nothing yet. It's all rather worrying.</li>\n<li>That we are all rather fragile.</li>\n<li>Pirates don't appreciate the scientific method.</li>\n<li>That I should have stayed at home.</li>\n<li>That my degree is worthless!</li>\n<li>The galaxy is a scary, scary place.</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223612,"modifiedTime":1662411891429,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"ZkPRrRVrG6GvBdS2","name":"Gambler","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>A fool and his money are soon parted. You're no fool, but in the gambling pits of the galaxy, like the fighting maze of Fellus IV or the aristocrat Sket racing of the Golden Station, there are many fools. You're good at finding a mark, and playing the odds in your favour.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A deck of holo cards, well-thumbed, nice clothes and a serious hat that marks you as a player. A roll of holofilm with your best cheats scribbled on it. A knife (S1d6+1P).</p>\n<p><strong>Who have you fleeced? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Brulian, a bounty hunter. Bad move.</li>\n<li>Your sister. Never liked her anyway.</li>\n<li>The first manifestation of the Sequined God, surprisingly bad at dice.</li>\n<li>Hemlock, a nice chap, prone to ranting.</li>\n<li>Captain Deq, decorated hero of the Nova Guard. A sore loser.</li>\n<li>Who haven't you fleeced?</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Who wants revenge? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Brulian, need to keep moving.</li>\n<li>Your old lover. Always been a sore loser.</li>\n<li>Your old shipmates, whom you had to trade for a throw of the dice.</li>\n<li>Lord Telleroz, and his robotic daughters.</li>\n<li>Your family. Turns out blood isn't thicker than water. Who knew?</li>\n<li>Who doesn't want revenge?</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223613,"modifiedTime":1662411891430,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"aVx0smyJX49joRxC","name":"Trader","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>Remember the buzz of that first sale when those Zelanquin monks bought some phase coils that had fallen off the back of a grav-van. Since then you've dragged yourself off the streets by your ability to smell a bargain and seal the deal. Quality merchandise, of course.</p>\n<p>Equipment: Travel robes, fake jewellery, independent trading licence, a stash of shoddy goods, ion-shot pistol up your sleeve (S1d6+1E).</p>\n<p><strong>What have you traded? (roll&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Holodisks from the pleasure pits of Ferrus.</li>\n<li>Feyworms from the jungles of Hetch, tasty!</li>\n<li>Robot parts from the gladiator ring of Steess</li>\n<li>Food parcels to the barren zone of Hespis IV.</li>\n<li>Entertainment databanks to the prisoners of Gekt III.</li>\n<li>Anything and everything!</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Who thinks you ripped them off? (roll&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Trot'ter Merchant Lords know you gave them dodgy holodisks.</li>\n<li>Big Bob blames you for a deal that went bad.</li>\n<li>The Merchant Combine want 'words' with you...</li>\n<li>You don't rip anyone off, you are a 'legitimate' business person.</li>\n<li>That gun you sold Ripper blew up, he's mad!</li>\n<li>House Hanabi got some goods off you that never showed up, not your fault!</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223615,"modifiedTime":1662411891431,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"delksFE5wd5UAPC9","name":"Mechanic","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>Grease Monkey, Tool Jockey, Tinkerer, you've heard all the nicknames. But when things need fixing, they all come to you. While some people are good at wielding a gun, you're better at fixing it, and some people fly the ship, but you make sure it stays together. You're an important part of any team, maybe the most important. And nobody, and I mean nobody should ever mess with your tools.</p>\n<p>Equipment: Magnetic boots, toolbelt with universal spanner, sub-space sealant, diagnostic scanner, assorted probes and couplings. A wrench (S1d6+1C).</p>\n<p><strong>Where's the best place you've worked? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Habitation domes during a meteor storm.</li>\n<li>Custom refit for a Rebel shuttle, Shhh!</li>\n<li>Space station Lupin 3, rush job. Won't last.</li>\n<li>Patching up haulers for the Merchant Combine.</li>\n<li>Demolishing a harvesting plant, some collateral damage, whoops!</li>\n<li>ZeroG sports stadium, paid with a season ticket.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What do you spend your money on? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Antique grav-bike, it's a beast.</li>\n<li>The Pleasure Hive, work hard, play hard.</li>\n<li>Betting on drakkon racing, can't give it up.</li>\n<li>Building robots to sell at auction. No refunds.</li>\n<li>Gravchute holidays in the Hoon Mountains.</li>\n<li>Black market Cadence, for your gran.</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223616,"modifiedTime":1662411891432,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"ecD8LWIvs1wzp6Oq","name":"Entertainer","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>You can hold a tune, play an instrument or tell a story, good enough that others will listen. People like you for that reason, and listen to what you have to say. Not that you take advantage of that. Not at all. But hey, everyone has to make a living right?</p>\n<p>Equipment: A neo-violin, stret-cordian or other musical instrument, a short sword (S1d6+2S) for effect, nice clothes and a jaunty hat that marks you as someone to watch. A datapad with the heavily annotated play you've been working on.</p>\n<p><strong>Who you have entertained? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The crowds outside the grand palace on the Jewel of the Chorus.</li>\n<li>The patrons of the floating Skyswallow opera house.</li>\n<li>The penitentiary staff of Ronus IV.</li>\n<li>Barbarian Queen Tamulan's last party.</li>\n<li>No one, they are not yet ready for your greatness.</li>\n<li>Anyone who'll listen on the streets.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What have you learned? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Nova Guard are romantics at heart.</li>\n<li>Hafo Lux is a swindler.</li>\n<li>Great stories are often unappreciated.</li>\n<li>Poetry is not for you, but the peons love it.</li>\n<li>Sweet words hide ugly thoughts.</li>\n<li>There's money in well-spoken lies.</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223617,"modifiedTime":1662411891432,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"gxB6P43eU7dmSBc8","name":"Smuggler","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>You shouldn't have accepted that load off Spurious Gwang. Yes, you delivered it before the Nova Guard showed up but you can only push your luck so far before they wipe that cocky smile off your face. Contracts come your way because you don't ask questions but maybe you should, given how many times you ended up at the wrong end of a disrupter barrel.</p>\n<p>Equipment: Reinforced ex-service jacket (light armour), slug pistol (M1d6+2P), cigarillo, holo-cube of star maps, lucky charm.</p>\n<p><strong>What was your last run? (roll&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Medical supplies the Garron III rebels.</li>\n<li>Escapees from the Pleasure Hive orbiting Inux Prime.</li>\n<li>Relics excavated from sacred Karahus.</li>\n<li>Weapons scavenged from a graveyard of space wrecks.</li>\n<li>Robots liberated from the Eoroz factory moon.</li>\n<li>Food supplies to war-torn Wega through the orbital blockade.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What went wrong? (roll&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Attacked by a warp horror, ship damaged.</li>\n<li>Hijacked by rival, stole your load.</li>\n<li>Chitinous warp vermin overran the ship.</li>\n<li>Caught by pirates, chased through asteroids.</li>\n<li>Stowaway fugitives damaged the ship.</li>\n<li>Jettisoned shipment during Hegemony pursuit.</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223618,"modifiedTime":1662411891433,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"i0HBEX2pCx2LnABY","name":"Rebel","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>What will you stand for? What will you fight for? What will you die for? This is what motivates you from one escapade to the next. Anyone can die, but you'll die for a cause. With a quick wit, a fast trigger finger and a short lifespan; every cause needs a professional rebel to lend inspiration to the downfall of all cruel tyrants, corrupt oligarchs and bloodthirsty warlords.</p>\n<p>Equipment: scruffy but stylish attire, good luck charm, trusty laser pistol (S1d6+2E).</p>\n<p><strong>What is your cause? (roll&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Freedom. No person should be enslaved!</li>\n<li>Fame. Who cares who you fight for as long as they remember your name!</li>\n<li>Idealism. For the greater good!</li>\n<li>Patriotism. I wear this flag for a reason, pal!</li>\n<li>Money. Who cares as long as I get paid.</li>\n<li>Retired. I used to have a cause...but that was a long time ago...</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What rebellions did you fight in? (roll&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Skalliax Coup. A washout.</li>\n<li>The Kvis-Kor Uprising. Many friends died.</li>\n<li>The Liberation of Vallus, glorious!</li>\n<li>The Reclaimation of the Oostian Throne</li>\n<li>The Overthrowing of the Overlords of Jaarg.</li>\n<li>The Mundus Insurrection. The less said the better.</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223619,"modifiedTime":1662411891434,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"j2ef3vOD5jpQzYs4","name":"Soldier","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>Signed up, shipped out and shot at, it was never the life of glory and camaraderie you longed for. Did grinding those tours of duty change you or did the horrors of battle just make you realize the person you actually were all along? Well, you won't find the answers on that barstool and it sure doesn't banish the ghosts of your past. Best strap up and move out.</p>\n<p>Equipment: breastplate under reinforced greatcoat (modest armour), disrupter pistol (M1d6+1E), energy sword (M2d6E), squad tattoos, holo-locket of those loved and lost.</p>\n<p><strong>Where did you serve? (roll&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Muani tombworld, clearing scavengers.</li>\n<li>The privateer Azure Lady, raiding freighters under letters of marque.</li>\n<li>Defending the besieged Crystal Sky Citadel.</li>\n<li>Patrolling the jungles of Bulang Bulan.</li>\n<li>Boarding actions in deep space.</li>\n<li>The ill-fated Charge of the Clans in the forbidden zone on Damas IV.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Who did you serve under? (roll&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Hafo Lux, ruthless merchant prince.</li>\n<li>The Obsidian Warlords, cryptic and aloof.</li>\n<li>Your late father.</li>\n<li>House Freyne, but don't tell anyone</li>\n<li>The barbarian Queen Tamulan</li>\n<li>Blue Karew's mercenary battalion</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223620,"modifiedTime":1662411891435,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"jJjL17Dtv0b3ilCj","name":"Investigator","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>Space is a lawless place. Most, if not all law enforcement officers are firmly planted in the pocket of someone able to pay - but not you. You stand as the only form of justice in this sector. You've made a lot of enemies on both sides of the law and it's just a matter of time before you piss off the wrong person...</p>\n<p>Equipment: A skim-bike, your best friend. A datapad for recording notes on your targets and a smack gun (M2d6C) for taking them down when you finally get them. A trench coat and a pack of smoke-sticks just for show, of course. Universal translator implant.</p>\n<p><strong>What was your most difficult case? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Hound of the BaskerWorld.</li>\n<li>The Murder of The Scarlet Lady of House Renn.</li>\n<li>The Adventure of the Empty Ship.</li>\n<li>The Case of who stole my whiskey.</li>\n<li>The Embezzlement scandal at WeyCorp.</li>\n<li>I'm still waiting for my big break</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What keeps you on the right track? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>)</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>You were betrayed by your partner. Get even.</li>\n<li>Your lover died - no one else should suffer that.</li>\n<li>Inspired by your father, a great man.</li>\n<li>A criminal wronged you and local law did nothing.</li>\n<li>Corruption in the system makes you sick.</li>\n<li>It's just the right thing to do.</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223621,"modifiedTime":1662411891435,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"jpaxzz3eyA784wio","name":"Agitator","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>You spend your time stirring things up, digging into the psyche of the mob and twisting it to your ends. You are a good speaker, good at manipulating people, and at prodding the sore spots. That serf riot on Geddis IV? That was you. You had something to do with the overthrow of the Sequined God on Meblus III, some say. You don't comment.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A power baton (S1d6+1C), a hidden combat vest (light armour), pamphlets, seditious writings.</p>\n<p><strong>Who you've worked for (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Lord Tern of house D'leon, a psychopath.</li>\n<li>The Whisper Sect - bunch of warp crazies.</li>\n<li>Hafo Lux, stirring up trouble to crash prices.</li>\n<li>The priesthood of Sest, in the failed Krebix revolution.</li>\n<li>Lord Selext, in his mad war against the Hegemony.</li>\n<li>Resurrected Clan chief Heent, on Malbaadas II.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Who's hunting you? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]]).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Nova Guard, oh dear...</li>\n<li>The Merchant Combine, for no good reason.</li>\n<li>The Church of the God Betrayed.</li>\n<li>Your brother, the fool.</li>\n<li>Verlenti flesh eaters. They say you'd taste good.</li>\n<li>You don't know. Which is worrying.</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223623,"modifiedTime":1662411891436,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"stKEW4Q3yPboZTfo","name":"Raconteur","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>You can tell a good tale, that's for sure. Weave narrative like your life depended on it, and you have a good eye for what you audience wants to hear. Is it all true? Well, not exactly true. Like all great stories it has a life of it's own, so does that really matter? It seems to some, yes. Which is a shame, but there you go. Have I ever told you of the time I..?</p>\n<p>Equipment: Jaunty clothes, a bottle or two of something strong. An ornate laser pistol (S1d6+2E), few 'relics' of your past exploits, impressive but worthless.</p>\n<p><strong>What tales do you tell? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>War stories, from your Nova Guard days.</li>\n<li>Tales of exploration in Bulang Bulan.</li>\n<li>The latest tales from the Jewel of the Chorus.</li>\n<li>Gossip from the salons of Merchant Combine.</li>\n<li>Stories of pirates and Hafo Lux.</li>\n<li>Stuff you read in books, all true!</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Where have you been? (roll a&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Jewel of the Chorus, where you're well-known.</li>\n<li>Where haven't you been?</li>\n<li>Skalliax, you knew the infector.</li>\n<li>The liberation of Vallus, you served on ship.</li>\n<li>The great battle of Garron III!</li>\n<li>Here and there. Buy me a drink?</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223625,"modifiedTime":1662411891437,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"wG1a37942hDha6iV","name":"Street Kid","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>Wild-eyed and hungry, you beg, borrow and steal to survive, scowling and sneering at the high-born and moneyed from afar. You owe them nothing but contempt. Some nights you stare at the stars from the rooftops, wondering if there is a life up there for you.</p>\n<p>Equipment: Scruffy clothes, knife in boot (S1d6+1S), bedroll, a pouch of worthless but treasured things.</p>\n<p><strong>Where did you trespass? (roll&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The bubbling slime gardens of Yaffan 'Worm face'.</li>\n<li>The Chapel of the Rusted Guru, to hear the cyborg choir.</li>\n<li>Docking bay 12, to glimpse the star yacht of Grom the Elder.</li>\n<li>Club Amorous, where the dopey rich kids dance and debauch.</li>\n<li>Warehouse X-18, you swear you saw cylinders of glowing bodies.</li>\n<li>The lizard-bird aviary of Lady Hanabi, vicious things!</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Who almost caught you there? (roll&nbsp;<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark-tertiary);\" title=\"1d6\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\">1d6</a>).</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Garff, a friendly rival.</li>\n<li>Security robots, slow but relentless.</li>\n<li>The thief Karloi, you strayed on her patch.</li>\n<li>Ecker's Boys, thugs out to make menace.</li>\n<li>A curious xenopede, who followed you home.</li>\n<li>Your mother, and she wasn't proud or happy.</li>\n</ol>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":10},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":12},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223626,"modifiedTime":1662411891437,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
